        "data": {

                }
            }
        }
    }
}, {
    $unwind: "$data"
}, {
    $group: {
        "_id": {
            "key": "$_id",
            "field": {
                $arrayElemAt: [{
                    $split: ["$data.k", "|"]
                }, 0]
            },
            "time": {
                $arrayElemAt: [{
                    $split: ["$data.k", "|"]
                }, 1]
            }
        },
        "data": {
            $sum: "$data.v"
        }
    }
}, {
    $group: {
        "_id": {
            "key": "$_id.key",
            "time": "$_id.time"
        },
        "data": {
            $push: {

                v: "$data"
            }
        }
    }
}, {
    $project: {
        "data": 1,
        "_id": {
            $toInt: {
                $add: [
                    "$_id.key",
                    {
                        $multiply: [
                            {
                                $floor: {
                                    $divide: [{
                                        $toInt: "$_id.time"
                                    }, 100]
                                }
                            },
                            3600
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        $multiply: [
                            {
                                $mod: [{
                                    $toInt: "$_id.time"
                                }, 100]
                            },
                            60
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        
    }
}, {
    $replaceRoot: {
        newRoot: {
            $mergeObjects: [
                "$$ROOT",
                {
                    $arrayToObject: "$data"
                }
            ]
        }
    }
